  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter and ghee in a molcajete over medium heat.",
    "Add olive oil, then sauté chopped onion and minced garlic until softened.",
    "Add chopped carrots and cook for 5 minutes until they start to caramelize.",
    "Add crushed tomatoes, fish stock, and white fish. Cook for 8 minutes.",
    "Using a slotted spoon, remove the fish and blend the bisque with an immersion blender until smooth.",
    "Return the fish to the molcajete and add heavy cream and lemon juice. Simmer for 2 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Ladle the bisque into bowls and garnish with chopped parsley."
